  ! File format:
  !
  !  1: Block 1
  !  2: Block 2
  !  3: Block 3
  !       :
  !  N: Block N
  !

  ! Block format:
  !
  !     #byte  contents
  ! -------------------
  !  1:    8   block_size
  !  2:    1   var. type (b:byte, i:integer, w:real(wp), d:real(dp), s:real(sp))
  !  3:   40   tag name
  !  4:    n   payload
  !  5:    8   next common tag block pos. (zero => termiated)

